<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>皮蛋瘦肉粥 on 大大的小蜗牛</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/tags/%E7%9A%AE%E8%9B%8B%E7%98%A6%E8%82%89%E7%B2%A5/</link><description>Recent content in 皮蛋瘦肉粥 on 大大的小蜗牛</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><copyright>© 2006 - 2024 &lt;span class='inline-block'>&lt;a href='https://www.eallion.com/copyright/' target='_blank'>eallion.com&lt;/a> All Rights Reserved&lt;/span>. &lt;span class='inline-block'>&lt;a href='https://beian.miit.gov.cn/' target='_blank'>浙ICP备16031768号-2&lt;/a>&lt;/span></copyright><lastBuildDate>Thu, 07 Apr 2011 08:29:11 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.eallion.com/tags/%E7%9A%AE%E8%9B%8B%E7%98%A6%E8%82%89%E7%B2%A5/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>皮蛋瘦肉粥</title><link>https://www.eallion.com/pidanshourouzhou/</link><pubDate>Thu, 07 Apr 2011 08:29:11 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.eallion.com/pidanshourouzhou/</guid><description>这篇文章介绍了制作皮蛋瘦肉粥的步骤和一些改进备忘。制作过程包括将瘦肉腌制10分钟，煮开剩饭并熬制成稠状，切碎皮蛋和青菜，然后加入姜片、猪肉和皮蛋，最后加入青菜、盐、鸡精和胡椒粉搅拌均匀。文章还提到了几处改进备忘，如使用香菜代替青菜，使用鲜米代替剩饭等。还提到了在煮好的粥上面加鸡蛋和热油作为调味的改进方法。</description><media:content xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://www.eallion.com/pidanshourouzhou/featured.png"/></item></channel></rss>